710334,137,681,12,15,1,30,3,Athassa thinamiddhaṃ uppajjati. 
710335,137,681,16,50,1,221,27,"So‘‘ uppannaṃ me thinamiddhan’’ ti ñatvā udakena mukhaṃ puñchitvā, kaṇṇe ākaḍḍhitvā paguṇaṃ dhammaṃ sajjhāyitvā divā gahitaṃ vā ālokasaññaṃ manasikaritvā thinamiddhaṃ vinodetvā puna chandaṃ uppādetvā kammaṭṭhānaṃ manasi karoti. "
