711023,137,875,132,152,1,151,16,Apica annādīsu‘‘ evaṃ vaṇṇavantaṃ gandhavantaṃ rasavantaṃ phassasampannaṃ khādimha bhuñjimha pivimha paribhuñjimhā’’ ti kāmassādavasena kathetuṃ na vaṭṭati. 
