711050,137,882,2,14,1,50,6,1081. Dutiyassa paṭhame bārāṇasiyan ti evaṃnāmake nagare. 
711051,137,882,15,26,1,119,10,Isipatane {migadāye}ti isīnaṃ patanuppatanavasena evaṃladdhanāme migānaṃ abhayadānavasena dinnattā migadāyasaṅkhāte ārāme. 
711052,137,882,27,36,1,89,8,"Ettha hi uppannuppannā sabbaññuisayo patanti, dhammacakkappavattanatthaṃ nisīdantīti attho. "
711053,137,882,37,68,1,319,25,"Nandamūlakapabbhārato sattāhaccayena nirodhasamāpattito vuṭṭhitā anotattadahe katamukhadhovanādikiccā ākāsena āgantvā paccekabuddhaisayopettha otaraṇavasena patanti, uposathatthañca anuposathatthañca sannipatanti, gandhamādanaṃ paṭigacchantāpi tatova uppatantīti iminā isīnaṃ patanuppatanavasena taṃ‘‘ isipatanan’’ ti vuccati. "
711054,137,883,2,48,1,532,45,{Āmantesī}ti dīpaṅkarapādamūle katābhinīhārato paṭṭhāya pāramiyo pūrento anupubbena pacchimabhave katābhinikkhamano anupubbena bodhimaṇḍaṃ patvā tattha aparājitapallaṅke nisinno mārabalaṃ bhinditvā paṭhamayāme pubbenivāsaṃ anussaritvā majjhimayāme dibbacakkhuṃ visodhetvā pacchimayāmāvasāne dasasahassilokadhātuṃ unnādento sabbaññutaṃ patvā satta sattāhāni bodhimaṇḍe vītināmetvā mahābrahmunā āyācitadhammadesano buddhacakkhunā lokaṃ voloketvā lokānuggahena bārāṇasiṃ gantvā pañcavaggiye saññāpetvā dhammacakkaṃ pavattetukāmo āmantesi. 
711055,137,884,2,14,1,49,7,"Dveme , bhikkhave, {antā}ti dve ime, bhikkhave, koṭṭhāsā. "
711056,137,884,15,30,1,134,14,Imassa pana padassa saha samudāhārena samudāhāranigghoso heṭṭhā avīciṃ upari bhavaggaṃ patvā dasasahassilokadhātuṃ pattharitvā aṭṭhāsi. 
711057,137,884,31,46,1,151,13,"Tasmiṃyeva samaye aṭṭhārasakoṭisaṅkhā brahmāno samāgacchiṃsu, pacchimadisāya sūriyo atthameti, pācīnadisāya āsāḷhanakkhattena yutto puṇṇacando uggacchati. "
711058,137,884,47,63,1,96,10,"Tasmiṃ samaye bhagavā imaṃ dhammacakkappavattanasuttaṃ ārabhanto‘‘ dveme, bhikkhave, antā’’ tiādimāha. "
711059,137,885,2,9,1,62,5,Tattha {pabbajitenā}ti gihisaṃyojanaṃ chinditvā pabbajjupagatena. 
711060,137,885,10,16,1,30,4,Na {sevitabbā}ti na vaḷañjetabbā . 
