711896,138,243,2,8,1,41,5,"Sabbepi pannabhārā te, katakiccā anāsavāti. "
711897,138,244,2,4,1,18,2,Ayaṃ dutiyasaṅgīti. 
711898,138,245,2,21,1,127,15,Evamimaṃ dutiyasaṅgītiṃ saṅgāyitvā therā‘‘ uppajjissati nu kho anāgatepi sāsanassa evarūpaṃ abbudan’’ ti olokayamānā imaṃ addasaṃsu–
711899,138,245,22,37,1,117,13,‘‘ ito vassasatassa upari aṭṭhārasame vasse pāṭaliputte dhammāsoko nāma rājā uppajjitvā sakalajambudīpe rajjaṃ kāressati. 
711900,138,245,38,44,1,63,6,So buddhasāsane pasīditvā mahantaṃ lābhasakkāraṃ pavattayissati. 
711901,138,245,45,55,1,93,10,Tato titthiyā lābhasakkāraṃ patthayamānā sāsane pabbajitvā sakaṃ sakaṃ diṭṭhiṃ paridīpessanti. 
711902,138,245,56,64,1,44,6,Evaṃ sāsane mahantaṃ abbudaṃ uppajjissatī’’ ti. 
711903,138,245,65,68,1,20,3,Atha nesaṃ etadahosi–
711904,138,245,69,85,1,75,11,"‘‘ kinnu kho mayaṃ etasmiṃ abbude uppanne sammukhā bhavissāma, na bhavissāmā’’ ti. "
711905,138,245,86,122,1,279,31,Atha te sabbeva tadā attano asammukhabhāvaṃ ñatvā‘‘ ko nu kho taṃ adhikaraṇaṃ vūpasametuṃ samattho bhavissatī’’ ti sakalaṃ manussalokaṃ chakāmāvacaradevalokañca olokentā na kañci disvā brahmaloke tissaṃ nāma mahābrahmānaṃ addasaṃsu parittāyukaṃ uparibrahmalokūpapattiyā bhāvitamaggaṃ. 
711906,138,245,123,126,1,23,3,Disvāna nesaṃ etadahosi–
711907,138,245,127,145,1,129,14,"‘‘ sace mayaṃ etassa brahmuno manussaloke nibbattanatthāya ussāhaṃ kareyyāma, addhā esa moggalibrāhmaṇassa gehe paṭisandhiṃ gahessati. "
711908,138,245,146,152,1,50,6,Tato ca mantehi palobhito nikkhamitvā pabbajissati. 
711909,138,245,153,171,1,148,16,So evaṃ pabbajitvā sakalaṃ buddhavacanaṃ uggahetvā adhigatapaṭisambhido hutvā titthiye madditvā taṃ adhikaraṇaṃ vinicchitvā sāsanaṃ paggaṇhissatī’’ ti. 
711910,138,246,2,8,1,53,6,Te brahmalokaṃ gantvā tissaṃ mahābrahmānaṃ etadavocuṃ–
711911,138,246,9,20,1,77,9,‘‘ ito vassasatassa upari aṭṭhārasame vasse sāsane mahantaṃ abbudaṃ uppajjissati. 
711912,138,246,21,35,1,151,14,Mayañca sakalaṃ manussalokaṃ chakāmāvacaradevalokañca olokayamānā kañci sāsanaṃ paggahetuṃ samatthaṃ adisvā brahmalokaṃ vicinantā bhavantameva addasāma. 
711913,138,246,36,50,1,88,10,"Sādhu, sappurisa, manussaloke nibbattitvā dasabalassa sāsanaṃ paggaṇhituṃ paṭiññaṃ dehī’’ ti. "
711914,138,247,2,34,1,176,22,"Evaṃ vutte mahābrahmā,‘‘ ahaṃ kira sāsane uppannaṃ abbudaṃ sodhetvā sāsanaṃ paggahetuṃ samattho bhavissāmī’’ ti haṭṭhapahaṭṭho udaggudaggo hutvā,‘‘ sādhū’’ ti paṭissuṇitvā paṭiññaṃ adāsi. "
711915,138,247,35,42,1,56,7,Therā brahmaloke taṃ karaṇīyaṃ tīretvā puna paccāgamiṃsu. 
711916,138,248,2,24,1,169,20,"Tena kho pana samayena siggavatthero ca caṇḍavajjitthero ca dvepi navakā honti daharabhikkhū tipiṭakadharā pattapaṭisambhidā khīṇāsavā, te taṃ adhikaraṇaṃ na sampāpuṇiṃsu. "
711917,138,248,25,44,1,96,14,"Therā‘‘ tumhe, āvuso, amhākaṃ imasmiṃ adhikaraṇe no sahāyakā ahuvattha, tena vo idaṃ daṇḍakammaṃ hotu–"
711918,138,248,45,71,1,167,20,"‘ tisso nāma brahmā moggalibrāhmaṇassa gehe paṭisandhiṃ gaṇhissati, taṃ tumhākaṃ eko nīharitvā pabbājetu, eko buddhavacanaṃ uggaṇhāpetū’’’ ti vatvā sabbepi yāvatāyukaṃ ṭhatvā– "
