711929,138,259,2,2,1,18,1,Tatiyasaṅgītikathā 
711930,138,260,2,11,1,88,9,Tissopi kho mahābrahmā brahmalokato cavitvā moggalibrāhmaṇassa gehe paṭisandhiṃ aggahesi. 
711931,138,260,12,22,1,96,10,Siggavattheropi tassa paṭisandhiggahaṇato pabhuti satta vassāni brāhmaṇassa gehaṃ piṇḍāya pāvisi. 
711932,138,260,23,31,1,69,8,Ekadivasampi uḷuṅkamattaṃ vā yāguṃ kaṭacchumattaṃ vā bhattaṃ nālattha. 
711933,138,260,32,47,1,85,10,"Sattannaṃ pana vassānaṃ accayena ekadivasaṃ‘‘ aticchatha, bhante’’ ti vacanamattaṃ alattha. "
711934,138,260,48,71,1,134,17,"Taṃdivasameva brāhmaṇopi bahiddhā kiñci karaṇīyaṃ katvā āgacchanto paṭipathe theraṃ disvā,‘‘ bho pabbajita, amhākaṃ gehaṃ agamitthā’’ ti āha."
711935,138,260,72,82,1,24,4,"‘‘ Āma, brāhmaṇa, agamimhā’’ ti."
711936,138,260,83,92,1,22,4,‘‘ Api kiñci labhitthā’’ ti?
711937,138,260,93,103,1,24,4,"‘‘ Āma, brāhmaṇa, labhimhā’’ ti. "
711938,138,260,104,108,1,22,4,So gehaṃ gantvā pucchi–
711939,138,260,109,118,1,35,5,‘‘ tassa pabbajitassa kiñci adatthā’’ ti?
711940,138,260,119,127,1,18,4,‘‘ Na kiñci adamhā’’ ti. 
711941,138,260,128,141,1,86,9,Brāhmaṇo dutiyadivase gharadvāreyeva nisīdi‘‘ ajja pabbajitaṃ musāvādena niggahessāmī’’ ti. 
711942,138,260,142,147,1,51,5,Thero dutiyadivase brāhmaṇassa gharadvāraṃ sampatto. 
711943,138,260,148,152,1,31,4,Brāhmaṇo theraṃ disvāva evamāha–
711944,138,260,153,166,1,64,9,‘‘ tumhe hiyyo amhākaṃ gehe kiñci aladdhāyeva‘ labhimhā’ ti avocuttha. 
711945,138,260,167,175,1,35,6,Vaṭṭati nu kho tumhākaṃ musāvādo’’ ti! 
711946,138,260,176,178,1,9,2,Thero āha–
711947,138,260,179,202,1,123,15,"‘‘ mayaṃ, brāhmaṇa, tumhākaṃ gehe satta vassāni‘ aticchathā’ ti vacanamattampi alabhitvā hiyyo‘ aticchathā’ ti vacanamattaṃ labhimha; "
711948,138,260,203,210,1,45,5,athetaṃ paṭisanthāraṃ upādāya evamavocumhā’’ ti. 
711949,138,261,2,4,1,16,2,Brāhmaṇo cintesi–
711950,138,261,5,49,1,270,31,"‘‘ ime paṭisanthāramattampi labhitvā‘ labhimhā’ ti pasaṃsanti, aññaṃ kiñci khādanīyaṃ bhojanīyaṃ labhitvā kasmā na pasaṃsantī’’ ti pasīditvā attano atthāya paṭiyāditabhattato kaṭacchumattaṃ bhikkhaṃ tadupiyañca byañjanaṃ dāpetvā‘‘ imaṃ bhikkhaṃ sabbakālaṃ tumhe labhissathā’’ ti āha . "
711951,138,261,50,65,1,153,15,So punadivasato pabhuti upasaṅkamantassa therassa upasamaṃ disvā bhiyyosomattāya pasīditvā theraṃ niccakālaṃ attano ghare bhattavissaggakaraṇatthāya yāci. 
711952,138,261,66,78,1,106,12,Thero adhivāsetvā divase divase bhattakiccaṃ katvā gacchanto thokaṃ thokaṃ buddhavacanaṃ kathetvā gacchati. 
711953,138,261,79,87,1,68,8,Sopi kho māṇavako soḷasavassuddesikoyeva tiṇṇaṃ vedānaṃ pāragū ahosi. 
711954,138,261,88,101,1,94,13,Brahmalokato āgatasuddhasattassa āsane vā sayane vā añño koci nisajjitā vā nipajjitā vā natthi. 
711955,138,261,102,114,1,98,11,"So yadā ācariyagharaṃ gacchati, tadāssa mañcapīṭhaṃ setena vatthena paṭicchādetvā laggetvā ṭhapenti. "
711956,138,261,115,117,1,13,2,Thero cintesi–
711957,138,261,118,136,1,106,14,"‘‘ samayo dāni māṇavakaṃ pabbājetuṃ, cirañca me idhāgacchantassa, na ca kāci māṇavakena saddhiṃ kathā uppajjati. "
711958,138,261,137,162,1,167,23,Handa dāni iminā upāyena pallaṅkaṃ nissāya uppajjissatī’’ ti gehaṃ gantvā yathā tasmiṃ gehe ṭhapetvā māṇavakassa pallaṅkaṃ aññaṃ na kiñci āsanaṃ dissati tathā adhiṭṭhāsi. 
711959,138,261,163,176,1,110,13,Brāhmaṇassa gehajano theraṃ disvā aññaṃ kiñci āsanaṃ apassanto māṇavakassa pallaṅkaṃ attharitvā therassa adāsi. 
711960,138,261,177,180,1,21,3,Nisīdi thero pallaṅke. 
711961,138,261,181,204,1,149,19,Māṇavakopi kho taṅkhaṇaññeva ācariyagharā āgamma theraṃ attano pallaṅke nisinnaṃ disvā kupito anattamano‘‘ ko mama pallaṅkaṃ samaṇassa paññapesī’’ ti āha. 
711962,138,262,2,9,1,68,7,Thero bhattakiccaṃ katvā vūpasante māṇavakassa caṇḍikkabhāve evamāha–
711963,138,262,10,25,1,45,8,"‘‘ kiṃ pana tvaṃ, māṇavaka, kiñci mantaṃ jānāsī’’ ti? "
711964,138,262,26,46,1,89,14,"Māṇavako‘‘ bho pabbajita, mayi dāni mante ajānante aññe ke jānissantī’’ ti vatvā, theraṃ pucchi–"
711965,138,262,47,56,1,28,5,‘‘ tumhe pana mantaṃ jānāthā’’ ti?
711966,138,262,57,69,1,42,6,"‘‘ Puccha, māṇavaka, pucchitvā sakkā jānitun’’ ti. "
711967,138,262,70,97,1,195,24,"Atha kho māṇavako tīsu vedesu sanighaṇḍukeṭubhesu sākkharappabhedesu itihāsapañcamesu yāni yāni gaṇṭhiṭṭhānāni, yesaṃ yesaṃ nayaṃ neva attanā passati nāpissa ācariyo addasa, tesu tesu theraṃ pucchi. "
711968,138,262,98,125,1,162,21,"Thero‘‘ pakatiyāpi tiṇṇaṃ vedānaṃ pāragū, idāni pana paṭisambhidāppatto, tenassa natthi tesaṃ pañhānaṃ vissajjane bhāro’’ ti tāvadeva te pañhe vissajjetvā māṇavakaṃ āha–"
711969,138,262,126,134,1,33,5,"‘‘ māṇavaka, ahaṃ tayā bahuṃ pucchito; "
711970,138,262,135,147,1,55,9,"ahampi dāni taṃ ekaṃ pañhaṃ pucchāmi, byākarissasi me’’ ti?"
711971,138,262,148,160,1,40,6,"‘‘ Āma, bho pabbajita, puccha byākarissāmī’’ ti. "
711972,138,262,161,166,1,36,5,Thero cittayamake imaṃ pañhaṃ pucchi–
711973,138,263,2,14,1,77,10,‘ ‘ Yassa cittaṃ uppajjati na nirujjhati tassa cittaṃ nirujjhissati nuppajjissati; 
711974,138,263,15,29,1,88,12,yassa vā pana cittaṃ nirujjhissati nuppajjissati tassa cittaṃ uppajjati na nirujjhatī’’ ti? 
711975,138,264,2,22,1,77,14,"Māṇavo uddhaṃ vā adho vā harituṃ asakkonto‘‘ kiṃ nāma, bho pabbajita, idan’’ ti āha."
711976,138,264,23,32,1,29,4,"‘‘ Buddhamanto nāmāyaṃ, māṇavā’’ ti."
711977,138,264,33,45,1,35,6,"‘‘ Sakkā panāyaṃ, bho, mayhampi dātun’’ ti."
711978,138,264,46,58,1,56,7,"‘‘ Sakkā māṇava, amhehi gahitapabbajjaṃ gaṇhantassa dātun’’ ti. "
711979,138,264,59,65,1,40,5,Tato māṇavo mātāpitaro upasaṅkamitvā āha–
711980,138,264,66,90,1,133,18,"‘‘ ayaṃ pabbajito buddhamantaṃ nāma jānāti, na ca attano santike apabbajitassa deti, ahaṃ etassa santike pabbajitvā mantaṃ uggaṇhissāmī’’ ti. "
711981,138,265,2,27,1,117,15,"Athassa mātāpitaro‘‘ pabbajitvāpi no putto mante gaṇhatu, gahetvā punāgamissatī’’ ti maññamānā‘‘ uggaṇha, puttā’’ ti anujāniṃsu. "
711982,138,265,28,34,1,63,6,Thero dārakaṃ pabbājetvā dvattiṃsākārakammaṭṭhānaṃ tāva ācikkhi. 
711983,138,265,35,42,1,66,7,So tattha parikammaṃ karonto nacirasseva sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahi. 
711984,138,265,43,46,1,18,3,Tato thero cintesi–
