715126,138,839,37,44,1,66,7,Gharadvāre ṭhitamattameva cassa bhagavantaṃ disvā parijano ārocesi. 
715127,138,839,45,67,1,139,16,"Brāhmaṇo satiṃ paṭilabhitvā saṃvegajāto sahasā vuṭṭhāya mahārahaṃ āsanaṃ paññapetvā bhagavantaṃ paccuggamma‘‘ ito, bhagavā, upasaṅkamatū’’ ti āha. "
