715130,138,839,86,89,1,24,3,Ito paraṃ uttānatthameva. 
715131,138,840,2,6,1,21,4,Yaṃ pana brāhmaṇo āha–
715132,138,840,7,19,1,35,7,"‘‘ apica yo deyyadhammo, so na dinno’’ ti. "
715133,138,840,20,50,1,246,25,"Tatrāyamadhippāyo – mayā nimantitānaṃ vassaṃvutthānaṃ tumhākaṃ temāsaṃ divase divase pāto yāgukhajjakaṃ, majjhanhike khādanīyabhojanīyaṃ, sāyanhe anekavidha pānavikati gandhapupphādīhi pūjāsakkāroti evamādiko yo deyyadhammo dātabbo assa, so na dinnoti. "
715134,138,840,51,60,1,59,9,Tañca kho no asantan ti ettha pana liṅgavipallāso veditabbo. 
715135,138,840,61,70,1,58,9,So ca kho deyyadhammo amhākaṃ no asantoti ayañhettha attho. 
715136,138,840,71,87,1,97,14,"Atha vā yaṃ dānavatthuṃ mayaṃ tumhākaṃ dadeyyāma, tañca kho no asantanti evamettha attho veditabbo. "
715137,138,841,2,13,1,84,8,"Nopi {adātukamyatā}ti adātukāmatāpi no natthi, yathā pahūtavittūpakaraṇānaṃ maccharīnaṃ. "
715138,138,841,14,49,1,240,31,"Taṃ kutettha labbhā bahukiccā {gharāvāsā}ti tatrāyaṃ yojanā– yasmā bahukiccā gharāvāsā, tasmā ettha santepi deyyadhamme dātukamyatāya ca taṃ kuto labbhā kuto taṃ sakkā laddhuṃ, yaṃ mayaṃ tumhākaṃ deyyadhammaṃ dadeyyāmāti gharāvāsaṃ garahanto āha. "
715139,138,841,50,70,1,103,14,"So kira mārena āvaṭṭitabhāvaṃ na jānāti,‘‘ gharāvāsapalibodhena me satisammoso jāto’’ ti maññi, tasmā evamāha. "
715140,138,841,71,86,1,93,12,"Apica– taṃ kutettha {labbhā}ti imasmiṃ temāsabbhantare yamahaṃ tumhākaṃ dadeyyaṃ, taṃ kuto labbhā? "
