717416,138,1272,2,2,1,23,1,Pañcavīsatiavahārakathā 
717417,138,1273,2,13,1,91,11,Apica imāni cha padāni vaṇṇentena pañca pañcake samodhānetvā pañcavīsati avahārā dassetabbā. 
717418,138,1273,14,21,1,58,7,Evaṃ vaṇṇayatā hi idaṃ adinnādānapārājikaṃ suvaṇṇitaṃ hoti. 
717419,138,1273,22,28,1,65,6,Imasmiñca ṭhāne sabbaaṭṭhakathā ākulā luḷitā duviññeyyavinicchayā. 
717420,138,1273,29,72,1,269,31,"Tathā hi sabbaaṭṭhakathāsu yāni tāni pāḷiyaṃ‘‘ pañcahākārehi adinnaṃ ādiyantassa āpatti pārājikassa, parapariggahitañca hotī’’ tiādinā nayena avahāraṅgāni vuttāni, tānipi gahetvā katthaci ekaṃ pañcakaṃ dassitaṃ, katthaci‘‘ chahākārehī’’ ti āgatehi saddhiṃ dve pañcakāni dassitāni. "
717421,138,1273,73,78,1,27,5,Etāni ca pañcakāni na honti. 
717422,138,1273,79,90,1,67,10,"Yattha hi ekekena padena avahāro sijjhati, taṃ pañcakaṃ nāma vuccati. "
717423,138,1273,91,97,1,43,6,Ettha pana sabbehipi padehi ekoyeva avahāro. 
717424,138,1273,98,110,1,86,11,"Yāni ca tattha labbhamānāniyeva pañcakāni dassitāni, tesampi na sabbesaṃ attho pakāsito. "
717425,138,1273,111,117,1,67,6,Evamimasmiṃ ṭhāne sabbaaṭṭhakathā ākulā luḷitā duviññeyyavinicchayā. 
717426,138,1273,118,128,1,92,10,Tasmā pañca pañcake samodhānetvā dassiyamānā ime pañcavīsati avahārā sādhukaṃ sallakkhetabbā. 
717427,138,1274,2,16,1,119,8,"Pañca pañcakāni nāma– nānābhaṇḍapañcakaṃ, ekabhaṇḍapañcakaṃ, sāhatthikapañcakaṃ, pubbapayogapañcakaṃ , theyyāvahārapañcakanti. "
717428,138,1274,17,40,1,146,15,"Tattha nānābhaṇḍapañcakañca ekabhaṇḍapañcakañca‘‘ ādiyeyya, hareyya, avahareyya, iriyāpathaṃ vikopeyya, ṭhānā cāveyyā’’ ti imesaṃ padānaṃ vasena labbhanti. "
717429,138,1274,41,46,1,46,5,Tāni pubbe yojetvā dassitanayeneva veditabbāni. 
717430,138,1274,47,65,1,110,13,"Yaṃ panetaṃ‘‘ saṅketaṃ vītināmeyyā’’ ti chaṭṭhaṃ padaṃ, taṃ parikappāvahārassa ca nissaggiyāvahārassa ca sādhāraṇaṃ. "
717431,138,1274,66,72,1,67,6,Tasmā taṃ tatiyapañcamesu pañcakesu labbhamānapadavasena yojetabbaṃ. 
717432,138,1274,73,76,1,47,3,Vuttaṃ nānābhaṇḍapañcakañca ekabhaṇḍapañcakañca. 
717433,138,1275,2,4,1,26,2,Katamaṃ sāhatthikapañcakaṃ? 
717434,138,1275,5,17,1,73,7,"Pañca avahārā– sāhatthiko, āṇattiko, nissaggiyo, atthasādhako, dhuranikkhepoti. "
717435,138,1275,18,25,1,57,7,Tattha sāhatthiko nāma parassa bhaṇḍaṃ sahatthā avaharati. 
717436,138,1275,26,39,1,55,8,Āṇattiko nāma‘‘ asukassa bhaṇḍaṃ avaharā’’ ti aññaṃ āṇāpeti. 
717437,138,1275,40,63,1,146,17,"Nissaggiyo nāma antosuṅkaghāte ṭhito bahisuṅkaghātaṃ pāteti, āpatti pārājikassāti, iminā ca saddhiṃ‘‘ saṅketaṃ vītināmeyyā’’ ti idaṃ padayojanaṃ labhati. "
717438,138,1275,64,80,1,74,11,"Atthasādhako nāma‘‘ asukaṃ nāma bhaṇḍaṃ yadā sakkosi, tadā avaharā’’ ti āṇāpeti. "
