717641,138,1304,64,79,1,99,15,Paṃsuṃ pana kudālena vā hatthehi vā pacchiyā vā tahiṃ tahiṃ pātento payoge payoge dukkaṭaṃ āpajjati. 
717642,138,1304,80,95,1,116,13,"Sace pana sabbaṃ paṃsuṃ nīharitvā kumbhiṃ thalaṭṭhaṃ katvāpi lajjidhammaṃ āpajjati, uddharaṇadukkaṭaṃ desetvā muccati. "
717643,138,1304,96,107,1,97,9,"Atha pana saussāhova kumbhiṃ āmasati, uddharaṇadukkaṭaṃ paṭippassambhati, āmasanadukkaṭe patiṭṭhāti. "
