717645,138,1304,116,135,1,131,12,"Atha saussāhova kumbhiṃ phandāpeti, āmasanadukkaṭaṃ paṭippassambhati,‘‘ phandāpeti, āpatti thullaccayassā’’ ti vuttathullaccaye patiṭṭhāti. "
