718015,138,1364,52,63,1,46,7,Idha pana ekassapi vāhanikā‘‘ nāvā’’ tveva vuccati. 
718016,138,1364,64,72,1,67,8,Nāvāya nikkhittan ti yaṃkiñci indriyabaddhaṃ vā anindriyabaddhaṃ vā; 
718017,138,1364,73,78,1,57,5,tassa avahāralakkhaṇaṃ thalaṭṭhe vuttanayeneva veditabbaṃ. 
718018,138,1364,79,85,1,85,5,Nāvaṃ {avaharissāmī}tiādimhi ca dutiyapariyesanagamanaāmasanaphandāpanāni vuttanayāneva. 
718019,138,1364,86,108,1,118,18,"Bandhanaṃ {mocetī}ti ettha pana yā bandhane muttamatte ṭhānā na cavati, tassā bandhanaṃ yāva na muttaṃ hoti, tāva dukkaṭaṃ. "
