718035,138,1366,2,21,1,193,18,"Nikkujjitvā ṭhapitanāvāya pana mukhavaṭṭiyā phuṭṭhokāsova ṭhānaṃ, tassāpi pañcahākārehi ṭhānaparicchedaṃ ñatvā yato kutoci phuṭṭhokāsaṃ uddhañca kesaggamattaṃ atikkantamatte pārājikaṃ veditabbaṃ. "
