718091,138,1375,47,82,1,232,27,"Maggappaṭipanne yāne yānasāmiko kenacideva karaṇīyena orohitvā maggā okkanto hoti, athañño bhikkhu paṭipathaṃ āgacchanto ārakkhasuññaṃ passitvā,‘‘ yānaṃ avaharissāmī’’ ti ārohati, tassa payogaṃ vināyeva goṇā gahetvā pakkantā, avahāro natthi. "
