718231,138,1413,45,71,1,80,13,"Athāpi ābhogaṃ katvā gacchati‘‘ dehī’’ ti vutte‘‘ dassāmī’’ ti,‘‘ dehī’’ ti vutte dātabbameva. "
718232,138,1413,72,91,1,94,13,"Sace koci attano dhanaṃ datvā‘‘ bhikkhussa gantuṃ dethā’’ ti vadati, laddhakappameva, gantuṃ vaṭṭati. "
718233,138,1413,92,130,1,193,26,"Sace pana koci issarajātiko dhanaṃ adatvāva‘‘ bhikkhūnaṃ bhāgaṃ mā gaṇhathā’’ ti vāreti, araññapālā ca‘‘ mayaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ tāpasānañca bhāgaṃ agaṇhantā kuto lacchāma, detha, bhante’’ ti vadanti, dātabbameva. "
