718245,138,1418,2,11,1,108,9,Mariyādacchedane pana tattha jātakabhūtagāmena saddhimpi mariyādaṃ chindantassa adinnādānapayogattā dukkaṭaṃ. 
718246,138,1418,12,17,1,29,5,Tañca pana pahāre pahāre hoti. 
718247,138,1418,18,24,1,52,6,Antoṭhatvā bahimukho chindanto bahi antena kāretabbo. 
718248,138,1418,25,32,1,52,6,Bahi ṭhatvā antomukho chindanto antoantena kāretabbo. 
718249,138,1418,33,44,1,74,11,Anto ca bahi ca chinditvā majjhe ṭhapetvā taṃ chindanto majjhena kāretabbo. 
718250,138,1418,45,64,1,125,16,"Mariyādaṃ dubbalaṃ katvā gāvo pakkosati, gāmadārakehi vā pakkosāpeti, tā āgantvā khurehi mariyādaṃ chindanti, teneva chinnā hoti. "
718251,138,1418,65,81,1,122,14,"Mariyādaṃ dubbalaṃ katvā gāvo udake paveseti, gāmadārakehi vā pavesāpeti, tāhi uṭṭhāpitavīciyo mariyādaṃ bhinditvā gacchanti. "
718252,138,1418,82,102,1,110,14,"Gāmadārake vā‘‘ udake kīḷathā’’ ti vadati, kīḷante vā utrāseti, tehi uṭṭhāpitavīciyopi mariyādaṃ chinditvā gacchanti. "
718253,138,1418,103,121,1,133,15,"Antoudake jātarukkhaṃ chindati, aññena vā chindāpeti, tenapi patantena uṭṭhāpitavīciyo mariyādaṃ chinditvā gacchanti, teneva chinnā hoti. "
718254,138,1418,122,168,1,312,40,"Mariyādaṃ dubbalaṃ katvā taḷākarakkhaṇatthāya taḷākato nibbahanaudakaṃ vā niddhamanatumbaṃ vā pidahati, aññato gacchantaṃ vā udakaṃ yathā ettha pavisati, evaṃ pāḷiṃ vā bandhati, mātikaṃ vā ujukaṃ karoti, tassa uparibhāge ṭhitaṃ attano taḷākaṃ vā bhindati, ussannaṃ udakaṃ mariyādaṃ gahetvā gacchati, teneva chinnā hoti. "
718255,138,1418,169,173,1,56,4,Sabbattha nikkhantaudakagghānurūpena avahārena kāretabbo. 
718256,138,1419,2,7,1,54,5,Niddhamanapanāḷiṃ ugghāṭetvā nīharantassāpi eseva nayo. 
718257,138,1419,8,90,1,619,72,"Sace pana tena mariyādāya dubbalāya katāya attano dhammatāya āgantvā vā anāṇattehi gāmadārakehi āropitā vā gāviyo khurehi mariyādaṃ bhindanti, attanoyeva dhammatāya anāṇattehi vā gāmadārakehi udake pavesitā vīciyo uṭṭhāpenti, gāmadārakā vā sayameva pavisitvā kīḷantā uṭṭhāpenti antoudake vā rukkho aññena chijjamāno patitvā uṭṭhāpeti, uṭṭhāpitā vīciyo mariyādaṃ chindanti, sacepi mariyādaṃ dubbalaṃ katvā sukkhataḷākassa udakanibbahanaṭṭhānaṃ vā udakaniddhamanatumbaṃ vā pidahati, aññato gamanamagge vā pāḷiṃ bandhati, sukkhamātikaṃ vā ujukaṃ karoti, pacchā deve vuṭṭhe udakaṃ āgantvā mariyādaṃ bhindati, sabbattha bhaṇḍadeyyaṃ. "
718258,138,1420,2,20,1,125,16,"Yo pana nidāghe sukkhavāpiyā mariyādaṃ yāva talaṃ pāpetvā chindati, pacchā deve vuṭṭhe āgatāgataṃ udakaṃ palāyati, bhaṇḍadeyyaṃ. "
