718740,138,1515,18,40,1,141,20,"Tattha so taṃ maññamāno tan ti so avahārako yaṃ āṇāpakena nimittasaññaṃ katvā vuttaṃ, taṃ etanti maññamāno tameva avaharati, ubhinnaṃ pārājikaṃ. "
718741,138,1515,41,61,1,130,18,"So taṃ maññamāno aññan ti yaṃ avaharāti vuttaṃ, taṃ etanti maññamāno aññaṃ tasmiṃyeva ṭhāne ṭhapitaṃ avaharati, mūlaṭṭhassa anāpatti. "
