718744,138,1516,2,11,1,114,8,Itthannāmassa {pāvadā}tiādīsu eko ācariyo tayo buddharakkhita-dhammarakkhita-saṅgharakkhitanāmakā antevāsikā daṭṭhabbā. 
718745,138,1516,12,26,1,120,13,Tattha bhikkhu bhikkhuṃ {āṇāpetī}ti ācariyo kiñci bhaṇḍaṃ katthaci sallakkhetvā tassa haraṇatthāya buddharakkhitaṃ āṇāpeti. 
718746,138,1516,27,38,1,85,8,"Itthannāmassa {pāvadā}ti gaccha tvaṃ, buddharakkhita, etamatthaṃ dhammarakkhitassa pāvada. "
718747,138,1516,39,46,1,79,6,Itthannāmo itthannāmassa {pāvadatū}ti dhammarakkhitopi saṅgharakkhitassa pāvadatu. 
