718749,138,1516,70,78,1,61,7,Āpatti {dukkaṭassā}ti evaṃ āṇāpentassa ācariyassa tāva dukkaṭaṃ. 
718750,138,1516,79,95,1,99,13,"Sace pana sā āṇatti yathādhippāyaṃ gacchati, yaṃ parato thullaccayaṃ vuttaṃ, āṇattikkhaṇe tadeva hoti. "
718751,138,1516,96,124,1,159,22,"Atha taṃ bhaṇḍaṃ avassaṃ hāriyaṃ hoti, yaṃ parato‘‘ sabbesaṃ āpatti pārājikassā’’ ti vuttaṃ, tato imassa taṅkhaṇeyeva pārājikaṃ hotīti ayaṃ yutti sabbattha veditabbā. "
718752,138,1517,2,18,1,118,12,"So itarassa {ārocetī}ti buddharakkhito dhammarakkhitassa, dhammarakkhito ca saṅgharakkhitassa‘‘ amhākaṃ ācariyo evaṃ vadati–"
