719530,138,1686,2,5,1,22,3,Cattāro vaṇṇā vattanti; 
719531,138,1687,2,27,1,24,3,Nāsikaggeva bhikkhuno’’ ti.( visuddhi.1.219; paṭi. ma. aṭṭha.2.1.163); 
719532,138,1688,2,26,1,163,15,Sabbakāyappaṭisaṃvedī assasissāmi… pe… passasissāmīti {sikkhatī}ti sakalassa assāsakāyassa ādimajjhapariyosānaṃ viditaṃ karonto pākaṭaṃ karonto‘‘ assasissāmī’’ ti sikkhati. 
719533,138,1688,27,41,1,102,10,Sakalassa passāsakāyassa ādimajjhapariyosānaṃ viditaṃ karonto pākaṭaṃ karonto‘‘ passasissāmī’’ ti sikkhati. 
719534,138,1688,42,52,1,85,10,Evaṃ viditaṃ karonto pākaṭaṃ karonto ñāṇasampayuttacittena assasati ceva passasati ca; 
719535,138,1688,53,63,1,52,6,tasmā‘‘ assasissāmi passasissāmī’’ ti sikkhatīti vuccati. 
719536,138,1688,64,77,1,101,12,"Ekassa hi bhikkhuno cuṇṇavicuṇṇavisaṭe assāsakāye passāsakāye vā ādi pākaṭo hoti, na majjhapariyosānaṃ. "
719537,138,1688,78,85,1,57,6,"So ādimeva pariggahetuṃ sakkoti, majjhapariyosāne kilamati. "
719538,138,1688,86,93,1,45,6,"Ekassa majjhaṃ pākaṭaṃ hoti, na ādipariyosānaṃ. "
719539,138,1688,94,101,1,57,6,"So majjhameva pariggahetuṃ sakkoti, ādipariyosāne kilamati. "
